---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Background, technical skills, and areas of interest"
  locale="en"
>
  <Navbar locale="en" currentPath="about" />

  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="section-container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8">About Me</h1>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <Card>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Background</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-dark-text">
              <p>
                Originally from Ukraine, now living in Norway and pursuing an IT education while working in a software development environment.
              </p>
              <p>
                My primary focus is programming and building practical systems that solve real problems. I value hands-on experience and prefer learning through implementation rather than theory alone.
              </p>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </div>

        <!-- Technical Stack -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Technical Stack</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <Card>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Languages & Frameworks</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-dark-text">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  JavaScript / TypeScript
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Python
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  HTML / CSS
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  React
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Vue 3
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  PHP
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Laravel
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  NestJS
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Node.js
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  SQL
                </li>
              </ul>
            </Card>

            <Card>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Tools & Technologies</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-dark-text">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Git / GitHub
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  PowerShell & Bash
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Windows Server
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Active Directory
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Linux fundamentals
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  AI integration for productivity and development workflows
                </li>
              </ul>
            </Card>

            <Card>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Areas of Practice</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-dark-text">
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Web development
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Automation scripting
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                  Server environments and Active Directory
                </li>
              </ul>
            </Card>

            <Card>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4">Currently Learning</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-dark-text">
                <p>
                  Everything listed above is part of an ongoing learning process — I don't position myself as a master, but as someone committed to continuous growth.
                </p>
                <p class="font-semibold">Currently expanding my knowledge in:</p>
                <ul class="space-y-2">
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                    C#
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                    Database engineering
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                    Application design
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-accent">▸</span>
                    Solving real-world development challenges
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </Card>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Interests -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <Card>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Beyond Technology</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-dark-text">
              <p>
                Beyond technical work, I'm deeply interested in psychology and philosophy, particularly in how people think, make decisions, and interact with complex systems.
              </p>
              <p>
                These perspectives strengthen my analytical approach to engineering and help me design technology with greater awareness of human factors.
              </p>
              <p>
                Music is another important creative outlet — I play acoustic drums and explore electronic sound design. It offers a different mode of pattern recognition that complements my technical mindset.
              </p>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer locale="en" />
</Layout>
